title: tueman loan
author: tueman
pages:
#- Tutum Bank, G13 Tigerstaden.
24.04.2013 23:40
tueman loans 5d with 20% compound interest a week from Tutum Bank. tueman must pay back within the deadline (2 weeks, the 8th of May).

#- If tueman fails to pay within 2 weeks, a bounty will be set up. When caught tueman must repay the bounty to Tutum Bank. After the deadline the interest rate will be 40%, still compound.

#- If tueman fails to repay it’s theft.
This loan is seen as an asset for Tutum Bank and can therefore be sold.
By signing this book, tueman agrees on all of the terms.


